# iA Writer Location map for ia-attribute.sh
#
# SETUP: copy this file to `ia-attribute.locations.conf` (drop the .example),
# then add one line per folder you want to edit through attribution.
#
# Format:  <LocationName>=<absolute on-disk folder>
#   - <LocationName> MUST match the Location label shown in iA Writer's sidebar.
#   - The folder must also be added as a Location in iA Writer itself
#     (so the ia-writer:// write command can resolve the path).
#   - Longest matching path prefix wins when a file is under multiple entries.
#
# Examples (edit to your own folders, then delete these sample lines):
# Notes=/Users/you/Documents/Notes
# Inbox=/Users/you/Documents/Notes/Inbox
